<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لأنها جمعت بين ما لله وما للعبد.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">ثامنها:</span> <span class="c2">(الكنز)</span> لجمعها جميع معاني القرآن.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">تاسعها:</span> <span class="c2">(الكافية)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">عاشرها:</span> <span class="c2">(الأساس)</span> لأنها أصل القرآن.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">حادي عشرها:</span> <span class="c2">(النور)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">ثاني عشرها:</span> سورة <span class="c2">(الحمد)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">ثالث عشرها:</span> سورة <span class="c2">(الشكر)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">رابع عشرها:</span> سورة <span class="c2">(الحمد الأولى)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">خامس عشرها:</span> <span class="c2">(الحمد القصوى)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>